  ('Star Wars: Episode VI - Return of the Jedi', '1983-5-25','After rescuing Han Solo from the palace of Jabba the Hutt, the rebels attempt to destroy the second Death Star, while Luke struggles to make Vader return from the dark side of the Force.',121, '2.35 : 1'),
  ('Star Wars: The Force Awakens', '2015-12-18', 'Three decades after the defeat of the Galactic Empire, a new threat arises. The First Order attempts to rule the galaxy and only a ragtag group of heroes can stop them, along with the help of the Resistance.',138,'2.35 : 1');
